title: Soleil Moon Frye: Meet the Author
itunes:author: iBooks
itunes:subtitle: Let’s Get This Party Started!
itunes:summary: Author, actress, developer (Moonfrye), and mother Soleil Moon Frye discusses her new book, Let’s Get This Party Started! A DIY guide to throwing amazing kids’ parties, the book features party themes for fairies, pirates, the 80s, luaus, Halloween, and more.
